             was indicted for <rs id="t18300916-165-off849" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18300916-165-off849" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300916-165-off849" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18300916-165-cd850" type="crimeDate">6th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-165-off849 t18300916-165-cd850"></join>, 1 chaise, value 25l., and 1 cushion, value 15s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18300916-165-victim1440" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Evans
                  <interp inst="t18300916-165-victim1440" type="surname" value="Evans"></interp>
