                     <interp inst="t18300916-165-person1444" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , attorney, produced an office copy of an adjudication of the Insolvent Dcbtor's Court, made on the<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183009160084"></xptr>25th of May, directing the prisoner to be discharged after eight month's imprisonment, for contracting a fraudulent debt with John Evans.</p>
